title: High-Precision Protection Plates from Armox
text:
High-Precision Protection Plates from Armox 29 September 2015 by SSAB Print Email Company Details 
SSAB offers the Armox protection plate, with a precision guarantee for determining the thickness of heavy plate. 
Accuracy is achieved through the company's four-high rolling mill, which is designed for very-high precision products. Armox delivers optimal grade and dimensions for all applications, assuring the correct hardness, toughness and total weight requirements for equipment.
